Package org.jgrapht.graph

Interface GraphSpecificsStrategy<V,​E>

Type Parameters:
V - the graph vertex type
E - the graph edge type
All Superinterfaces:
java.io.Serializable
All Known Implementing Classes:
DefaultGraphSpecificsStrategy, FastLookupGraphSpecificsStrategy, SimpleIdentityDirectedGraphTest.IdentitySpecificsStrategy
public interface GraphSpecificsStrategy<V,​E>
extends java.io.Serializable
A graph specifics construction factory.

Such a strategy can be used to adjust the internals of the default graph implementations.

See Also:
FastLookupGraphSpecificsStrategy, DefaultGraphSpecificsStrategy
